snippet.title: Runa | Official Announcement Trailer | April 16 on Kickstarter
snippet.description:
Runa is an indie adventure inspired by classic and modern JRPGs, with turn-based battles, social sim, and a story driven sci-fantasy world. In development in Unreal Engine 5. Runa also features elemental puzzles and base building, as well as minigames like farming, fishing, and cooking.

April 16 on Kickstarter: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/runarpg/runa
Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2787850/Runa/
https://twitter.com/RunaRPG | https://discord.com/invite/rsUHhwmVVJ
